reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really great and super compact!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This projector works great, I've wanted one for a while and this one was recommended to me through a friend, and it's so good I felt it necessary to write a review for it. It can be connected via Wi-Fi or HDMI, the color saturation is good even if the room isn't very dark, which is something that even most monitors struggle with at times. It also has a built-in speaker that, while not great, works fine for an average room in case there aren't speakers available. It also doesn't hurt that it looks very cute, and the design is lightweight enough to make it super portable. Overall, 10/10, especially factoring in the price!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great small, portable projector
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I bought a projector for home use. It is very small and portable - I attached it to my camera tripod, as it has a screw port like a camera. The device has good light quality, for room use. It also has a speaker, which I can use, or an audio port to connect to a different speaker. It connects well, wirelessly, to an android phone or tablet. Via a HDMI cable, it connects to a computer - the full screen is shown. The focus lever works well for a sharp image. Pictures and video as displayed by the projector onto my wall pictured here.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Projector in Small Size
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. All I can say is wow. This projector is small and compact but puts out a stunning picture for its size. I love the ability to connect through WiFi but note that iOS won’t show copyright movies through WiFi but they play fine through a media/HDMI adapters(not a projector issue, it’s a copyright rule). I was looking for something more compact than our other projector but with a great picture and this fit the bill. It comes packaged well and easy to set up(only took 10 mins). Everything is included to start watching movies or streaming. I started with a picture on my wall and it was beautiful. I’m looking forward to taking this camping next summer and I will also be using it in our backyard. Who doesn’t like a good movie outside?

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This projector is excellent. I haven't purchased a projector screen yet, but even when projecting onto the wall or the ceiling, the picture quality is very good. Surprisingly good, especially considering how the projector is so small and very portable. I expect that it will be very useful on the go, indoors or even outdoors. The remote is quite responsive, and the projector is highly versatile, allowing for different functions including HDMI or USB connection or screen mirroring from my phone, laptop and other devices. It seems to be good construction as well. I'm happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Worth every penny
reviews.reviewText: At first when I got the projector I didn’t like it because I couldn’t mirror apps like Hulu or Max or even Netflix due to software that these apps use to prevent piracy. *eye roll* . So as a result you need either a fire stick, google cast , or a laptop that you can plug in. Luckily I had a chromecast to plug in. When I plugged the chromecast in the projector made a weird noise and powered off, it may have been a short circuit, but since then it’s been working fine. I would also say the sound isn’t too great and the device fans really loins and gets hot…so the lifespan is questionable. I’ve had the product for about two weeks. I wish it came with a stand.Now let’s get to the good. The quality of the projector is better than my Vizio smart tv, I’m extremely impressed. It feels like I’m in a movie theatre every time I use the projector in bed. It’s an enjoyable experience. Considering the price point I think the picture quality surpasses my expectations. There are a few hurdles to overcome with casting what you want to watch, so I definitely recommend getting a fire stick or chromecast to watch all your shows and movies. I will consider getting a sound bar and a stand in the future if my budget allows.If you’re looking for an inexpensive projector this is a great option just be cautious of the power issue and using a chromecast.

reviews.reviewTitle: 買って良かったです！安くて、画質もいいです。期待以上の品質に驚きました！
reviews.reviewText: プロジェクターの画質が素晴らしいです。映画を映す際に、クリアで鮮明な映像が楽しめます。期待以上の品質に驚きました！設置が非常に簡単でした。取扱説明書がわかりやすく、数分で映像を投影することができました。初心者でも安心して使えます。プロジェクターがコンパクトで軽量なので、持ち運びや収納が簡単です。使わないときは場所を取らずに片付けられるので、使い勝手がいいですね。この価格帯でこれだけの性能が得られるとは驚きです。他の製品と比較しても、コストパフォーマンスが非常に高いと感じています。
